\rho
 (x - R\sin\alpha)^{2} + y^{2} + (z - R\cos\alpha)^{2} \leq R^{2}, 
 x^{2} + y^{2} + z^{2} \leq 2xR\sin\alpha + 2zR\cos\alpha. 
 x = \rho \cos\theta \sin\phi,\qquad y = \rho \sin\theta \sin\phi,\qquad z = \rho \cos\phi, 
 \rho \leq 2R(\cos\theta \sin\phi \sin\alpha + \cos\phi \cos\alpha). 
 0 \leq \theta \leq 2\pi,\qquad 0 \leq \phi \leq \alpha,\qquad 0 \leq \rho \leq 2R(\cos\theta \sin\phi \sin\alpha + \cos\phi \cos\alpha). 
